main event: A Project Blue Book report from July 7, 1967, describes photographs of unidentified objects in the sky over a mountainous area in San Luis Obispo, California.
interesting points: The report mentions a total of 4 photographs of the unidentified objects., The photographs are black and white and depict a landscape with mountains and trees., The objects in the sky are not identified, leading to speculation of potential UFOs., The photographs do not contain human faces or identifiable individuals., The report is unclassified and comes from the Foreign Technology Division.
